flowchart TD
    A[HR: Maintain Employee Register] --> B[Accountant initiates Payroll Run for period]
    B --> C[System calculates Gross Salary per employee]
    C --> D[System calculates PAYE<br/>using configurable tax settings]
    C --> E[System calculates SSNIT<br/>Employee percent and Employer percent<br/>from configurable tax settings]
    C --> F[System calculates Other Deductions]
    D --> G[Generate Payslips]
    E --> G
    F --> G

    G --> H[Accountant reviews Payroll Run]
    H --> I{Approved?}
    I -- No, corrections needed --> B
    I -- Yes --> J[Post Payroll Journal<br/>Dr Salary Expense<br/>Dr Employer SSNIT Expense<br/>Cr Staff Salaries Payable<br/>Cr PAYE Payable<br/>Cr SSNIT Payable<br/>Cr Other Payroll Deductions Payable]

    J --> K[Employee Self-Service Portal:<br/>Payslip becomes available]
    J --> L[Accountant initiates Salary Payment Run]
    L --> M[Post Payment Journal<br/>Dr Staff Salaries Payable / Cr Bank]
    M --> P[Bank Reconciliation]

    J --> Q[PAYE Payable and SSNIT Payable<br/>feed Tax Reports and Filing Schedules]
    Q --> R[Accountant Task Centre:<br/>Upcoming tax deadlines, Payroll due dates]
